title: Chen Yue
text: Chen Yue is a Chinese female <a href="Track%20cycling">track cyclist</a>, and part of the national team. She competed in the <a href="2009%20UCI%20Track%20Cycling%20World%20Championships%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20team%20pursuit">team pursuit event</a> at the <a href="2009%20UCI%20Track%20Cycling%20World%20Championships">2009 UCI Track Cycling World Championships</a>.
